headline: Better AI Dividend Stock: Nvidia or Dominion
summary: Nvidia is a leading maker of the chips used to power artificial intelligence.  Dominion Energy is a high-yield electric utility, but it happens to operate in a region seeing huge AI growth.  Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) is pretty much the poster child of the AI industry, with Wall Street hanging on every word the management says.
